    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, add the <strong>cashew nuts</strong> and <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong> to a separate baking tray</p><p>Put them in the oven for 7 min or until slightly darkened in colour</p><p>Tip: Watch these like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p><p>Once toasted, remove the<strong> toasted nuts & seeds</strong> and set aside to cool</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
