      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong>,<strong> ginger </strong>and<strong> chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a small bowl with 2 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tsp]</span> <strong>brown</strong> <strong>sugar</strong> and 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Roll the <strong>lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p><p>Add the juice of the<strong> lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>straight into the bowl and whisk it all together – this is your <strong>chilli lime dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
