    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse the <strong>black beans</strong></p><p>Once the rice is tender, add the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>black beans </strong>to the pot and cook for a further 4 min</p><p>Drain the <strong>brown</strong> <strong>rice </strong>and<strong> black beans</strong> and allow to steam-dry for 1-2 min or until cooled slightly, before returning them both to the pot – this is your <strong>beany rice</strong></p>",
