    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Chop the <strong>cooled</strong> <strong>toasted nuts & seeds </strong>together coarsely (save a few whole cashew nuts for garnish!) – this is your <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>nut & seed mix</strong></p>",
