    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>roasted sweet potato</strong>, <strong>chilli lime dressing</strong>, most of the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> and the <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>nut & seed mix</strong> to the <strong>beany rice</strong> and mix together gently – this is your <strong>chilli lime sweet potato & rice salad</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved cashew nuts </strong>and <strong>remaining chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
